        "created_at": "2005-09-10T22:07:12.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This is probably one of the tools most expected in the LBA World.<br>\nI was talking to <span class=\"bbcode-b\">Yaz0r</span> and he send me his LBA2extViewer and he give me permission to release it here.<br>\nSo you can start venerate <span class=\"bbcode-b\">Yaz0r</span> for the GREAT HELP in the LBA Modification World.</p>\n<p><span class=\"bbcode-b\">Note: The program is leaking memory and the program could crash if you switch from the various maps.</span></p>\n<p><span alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" class=\"broken-image\" title=\"This image is broken\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-unlink svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#unlink\"></use></svg></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"bbcode-b\">Download:</span> <a href=\"http://www.lobitowebsite.com/_lbaprojects/LBA2extViewer.zip\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">LBA2extViewer.zip</a> [7,36 MB]</p>",
