        "created_at": "2005-09-10T22:31:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>- alexfont: THIS IS GREAT!!! Finally we have this thing! <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/fearful.png?v=12\" title=\":fearful:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":fearful:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>Now I can continue with my parallel LBA game on LBA 1 engine project, as I can now convert the LBA 2 desert island to isometric almost 1:1 well of course with the changes I need for my game. <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/wink.png?v=12\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":wink:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
